I will be reading back into the thread over the next few days, looking for anyones questions or suggestions I may have missed, and then I think I will try to pull all this info into a rational form to see if the invincible Zaphod would consider it as an article.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    <br>
